# Vulnerabilities in npm's own bundled packages (minimatch, tar).
# These are internal to the npm CLI tool and are not reachable from
# our running Express application. They would only matter if an
# attacker could run `npm install` inside the container, which is
# not possible in our production setup.
#
# Re-evaluate when the node:24-alpine base image ships npm with fixes.
